==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Daw
<hw>Daw</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Contr. fr. <er>Adaw</er>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>To rouse.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To daunt; to terrify.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>B. Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

